{"tid":1976490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球首例「屍傳人」！泰國法醫疑遭武肺死者感染後死亡","createTime":"2020-04-17T09:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T10:01:03.000Z","uid":14918,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0921cf43d0f3ad5d9ce5c9be2650dd9e4d9630","tid":1976490,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:32:52.000Z","msg":"英國《太陽報》等外媒報導，泰國曼谷RVT醫療中心的Won Sriwijitalai及海南醫學院的Viroj Wiwanitkit兩 位專家在《法醫與法律醫學雜誌》(the Journal of Forensic and Legal Medicine)中撰文指出，泰國一名法醫日前疑在接觸新武漢肺炎死者的遺體後感染後去世。<br />\n<br />\n文中稱，該名法醫確診前，武漢肺炎病毒尚未在泰國境內大規模擴散，因此他從其他活著的武肺確診者身上感染病毒的機率很小。如果屬實，這將全球首宗新冠肺炎死者死後病毒不滅、造成「屍傳人」的案例。<br />\n<br />\n文章中同時呼籲法醫人員工作時應提高警惕。不過報導同時引述 <span style=\"color: red;\">世界衛生組織的話說，武漢肺炎死者的遺體通常是沒有傳染性的</span>，除非是解剖 過程中處理不當。然而，世衛迄今仍無法確定新冠病毒究竟可以在死者體內存活多久。<br />\n<br />\nWHO又放流料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4e4318a6b97e1fdb9af0f6b587e48b30702c69","tid":1976490,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:35:43.000Z","msg":"希望香港林衛國法醫快點中招<br />\n<br />\n呢條仆街經常辱罵示威者<br />\n有簽咩反黑暴唔知咩撚<br />\n仲支持警暴"},{"pid":"fd750e24a0ba5fdb2c6f297bae74cce3c93dadbc","tid":1976490,"uid":102343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cx8eQmw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCx8eQmw.jpg&h=e658a097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係瘟疫公司升到呢個都基本上sure win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed64916803b67c5daaa69859a39fba2e5958968","tid":1976490,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:38:15.000Z","msg":"玩瘟疫公司去到呢步基本上已經嬴左"},{"pid":"439fac5f7eb7773df4737420b6c44863fdc7dbc7","tid":1976490,"uid":3